OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine and dry
OL,6,Fthrough the evening with hazy sunshine
OL,7,Fat times as patchy cloud builds from
OL,8,Fthe west. Clear spells overnight
OL,9,Fallowing temperatures to fall to low
OL,10,Fsingle figures in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day,
OL,13,Fwith only limited amounts of high
OL,14,Fcloud. With lighter winds and widely
OL,15,Fsunny skies, it will be feeling warmer
OL,16,Fthan on Tuesday for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
