OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FAnother warm day Thursday, with
OL,7,Fshowery outbreaks of rain by the
OL,8,Fevening. Cooler Friday, likely staying
OL,9,Fdry with sunny spells. Rain into
OL,10,FSaturday clearing to a generally
OL,11,Fbright day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
